### Common API Endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:5000/api/common

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000/health

### Register New User
POST http://localhost:5000/api/common/register
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

{
  "fullName": "John Smith",
  "email": "john@dispatchpro.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "phone": "+1 (555) 123-4567",
  "company": "DispatchPro Inc",
  "role": "admin"
}

### Login User
POST http://localhost:5000/api/common/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@dispatchpro.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Verify Token
GET http://localhost:5000/api/common/verify
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Forgot Password
POST http://localhost:5000/api/common/forgot-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john@dispatchpro.com"
}
